tissueExpression.summary: Normal tissues generally showed weak to moderate cytoplasmic and membranous staining. Leydig cells were strongly positive. Cells in the CNS were mainly negative.
Normal tissues generally showed weak to moderate cytoplasmic and membranous staining. Leydig cells were strongly positive. Cells in the CNS were mainly negative.
Most malignant cells displayed weak to moderate cytoplasmic immunoreactivity which in cases was combined with membranous positivity. Malignant gliomas and lymphomas were generally negative.
